        </p>
        <h3 id="letter">Letter</h3>
        <p>
          At the bottom center of every card there's a letter. They have a
          frequency distribution compatible with English word games.
        </p>
        <p>
          Here's the distribution compared to Scrabble, Words With Friends, and
